gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br><br>Faedaer Ryverwalker<br>Raidmaster<br><br>(Side note: When we get in our 50's, if we need to switch to Kael faction, raids will be done to do that. There are places to hunt in Kael, Skyshrine, Thurg, that'll switch our faction around rather quickly. Killing a dragon in Velious will make us very friendly with Kael. For now, though, we're on CoV-Coldain.) <p></p><span class=m><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ufaedaerryverwalker.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Faedaer Ryverwalker</A> at: 7/5/02 3:19:25 pm<br></i></span><hr size=1><span class=m> Posts: <b>223</b>  </span></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td colspan=2><table cellpadding=8 cellspacing=0 width=100%><tr><td nowrap width=20% valign=top><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ufaedaerryverwalker.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Faedaer Ryverwalker</A> </span><br> <span class=usertitle>Raid Master</span><br> <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/fanimawizzy/Faegif.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top width=80% class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_exclamation_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Alternate character faction</span><br><span class=m><font color=#778899>Posted: 7/5/02 3:27:14 pm</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>    <hr size=1> For anyone that's taken the time and effort to kill enough giants to ally with Coldain and CoV, you know it can be a long and tedious process unless you're relying on the Arena to do most of the work. <br>So, with your alternate characters, you can -if you wish- go with the giants. Just be aware that once you hit 50 or so, you will have to switch back to CoV/Coldain faction if you wish to bring your alt on raids in Velious. If you go with giants, and kill dorfs to do it, you'll also be KoS to ThurgB and I have yet to find a way to fix this. Maybe the really high-end mobs in Kael give Dain faction hits, but I haven't ever got one. Our alts are around to break the tedium we sometimes feel with our mains, and if you're like me, Velious is a fun place to hunt. Plus there's some sweet gear in Skyshrine <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> . The dorfs drop pretty decent stuff as well. <p>Faedaer Ryverwalker<BR>Siege Captain<BR>Keeper of the Fist <BR>Woodland Priest of Tunare<BR></p><span class=m><i></i></span><hr size=1><span class=m> Posts: <b>827</b>  </span></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td colspan=2><table cellpadding=8 cellspacing=0 width=100%><tr><td nowrap width=20% valign=top><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/udadalanlyfrender.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dadalan Lyfrender</A> </span><br> <span class=usertitle>Raid Lieutenant</span><br> <BR><img src=http://mywebpages.comcast.net/bhoward3/images/Dad_headshot.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top width=80% class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_exclamation_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Velious faction(update)</span><br><span class=m><font color=#778899>Posted: 7/15/02 11:17:36 am</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>    <hr size=1> The 3 big boys of Velious: Tormax, Yelinak, and the Dain, are all on their own little faction triangle. You can kill mobs and do quests to raise them, but the amount is usually tiny. The only way to really get a good dent in these factions is to kill their enemy...<br><br>Killing Tormax will give a big hit to Dain and Yelinak<br>Killing Yelinak will give a big hit to Tormax<br>Killing Dain will give a big hit to Tormax<br><br>According to what I've read on velious faction discussions, killing any of them will knock your faction up with their enemies by at least one level per each death.<br><br>Just a little info that I found that I thought I'd share. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>-- <br>Baron Inien Astralwrath <br>Channeler of the 4th Rank<br>Elder of the Arcane Order <br>Shadows of the Ebon Moon - Vazaelle <p><br><br><a href="http://eq.guildmagic.com/character.cfm?ID=127031" target="_blank"><img src="http://mywebpages.comcast.net/bhoward3/images/dadalan.jpg" height=85 width=468 alt="Dadalan Lyfrender" border=0></a></p><span class=m><i></i></span><hr size=1><span class=m> Posts: <b>575</b>  </span></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></td></tr></table><br><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/febonmoonfrm5.emailToFriend?topicID=54.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/email.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="email this topic to a friend" align=absmiddle></a> Email This To a Friend </td><td align=right valign="top"></td></tr></table><table width="95%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td bgcolor=#006400><table border=0 width=100% cellpadding="5" cellspacing="1"><tr><td nowrap bgcolor=#000000 width=20%><a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/febonmoonfrm5.showAddTopicScreenFromWeb><img src=http://ebonmoon.com/images/Icons/newtopic.gif border=0 alt="New Topic"></a>  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/febonmoonfrm5.showAddPollScreenFromWeb><img src=http://ebonmoon.com/images/Icons/newpoll.gif border=0 alt="New Poll"></a> </td><td bgcolor=#000000><a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/febonmoonfrm5.threadControl?topicID=54.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/black_default/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image" align=absmiddle></a> Topic Commands (Moderator Only)  <br><a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/febonmoonfrm5.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=54.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receiv